description: The image shows a group of six people gathered in what appears to be a conference or meeting room with white walls and tiled flooring. A man in a salmon-colored sweater and jeans is standing, gesturing toward a laptop on a small round table, apparently presenting. The other five people are seated or standing around him, listening. All of them are wearing lanyards. Behind the group, there is a water cooler with the text "MGM GRAND" visible on it. To the left, a Puma backpack is partially visible. The text on the laptop screen is too small to be clearly read.
